Where does my information go?
Your personal information may be stored and processed in any country where we have facilities or service providers, and by using our service or by providing consent to us (where required by law), you agree to transferring information to countries outside of your country of residence, including to the United States, which may provide for different data protection rules than in your country. All Dotdigital entities operate under Standard Contractual Clauses and applicable measures of the GDPR providing protections and safeguards for cross-border transfers. We take all steps reasonably necessary to ensure that your data is treated securely and under this privacy policy.
